BACKEND API ENDPOINTS â€” BUILD ALL
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

Auth:
  POST /api/auth/login
  POST /api/auth/register
  POST /api/auth/refresh-token

Cases:
  GET    /api/cases             (list, filterable by district/disease/date)
  POST   /api/cases             (report new case)
  PUT    /api/cases/:id         (update case status)
  DELETE /api/cases/:id         (admin only)

Alerts:
  GET    /api/alerts            (feed, filterable by severity)
  POST   /api/alerts            (create manual alert)
  PUT    /api/alerts/:id/acknowledge
  POST   /api/alerts/:id/dispatch   (send SMS/email/push)

Water Quality:
  GET    /api/water/sensors          (all sensor readings)
  POST   /api/water/manual-report    (ASHA manual upload)
  GET    /api/water/history/:sensorId

AI/ML:
  GET    /api/ml/risk-score/:districtId   (current outbreak risk)
  GET    /api/ml/forecast/:districtId     (7-day prediction)
  GET    /api/ml/hotspots                 (geographic clustering)

Doctors:
  GET    /api/doctors
  POST   /api/doctors          (admin add)
  PUT    /api/doctors/:id
  DELETE /api/doctors/:id

Dashboard:
  GET    /api/dashboard/kpis          (live KPI numbers)
  GET    /api/dashboard/heatmap       (grid data for map)
  GET    /api/dashboard/trends        (7-day chart data)

WebSocket:
  ws://host/live     (real-time case + alert updates)

